$ Microsoft Power BI
@ Power BI

{ Components

  Power BI consists of three basic and two supplemental components:
  table { ll
     → Microsoft/products/Power/BI/Desktop ☰ An Windows desktop application, installed locally on a PC
     Power BI service ☰ A → development/Cloud/aaS/SaaS[SaaS]
     Power BI mobile apps ☰ Apps for Windows, iOS and → development/Android devices
     Power BI Reports Builder ☰ Create paginated reports.
     Power BI Report Server ☰ An on-premise report server where Power BI reports are published
  table }

}

{ Supported languages

  Microsoft Power BI supports two languages:
    • → Microsoft/Power-Query/M-formula/language
    • DAX (Data Analysis Expression)

}

